data.description: Finding the perfect countryside retreat is like stumbling upon a hidden gem in a bustling city. Just as a serene countryside lifestyle offers a tranquil escape from the chaos of urban living, this picturesque 7-acre farm presents a beautifully crafted Amish barn with 4 stalls, 5-6 fenced working pastures, and a charming upgraded home. Like a peaceful porch that wraps around the house, providing a haven for relaxation, this property invites you to soak in the breathtaking views, much like a scenic rooftop oasis amidst the hustle and bustle of the city.
